without all the details.

00:18:05.053 --> 00:18:06.219 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:18:06.988 --> 00:18:10.324 position:7% line:83% align:start
[CASSEROLE] One of the bandits
was carrying this sword.

00:18:10.457 --> 00:18:12.694 position:5% line:89% align:start
It also bears your family crest.

00:18:12.827 --> 00:18:14.094 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[gasps]
-[gasps]

00:18:14.227 --> 00:18:16.263 position:16% line:89% align:start
Sir, that's one of ours.

00:18:16.396 --> 00:18:17.799 position:41% line:83% align:start
[RETES]
They've got me.

00:18:18.365 --> 00:18:19.801 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's pretty clear,

00:18:19.934 --> 00:18:23.004 position:10% line:83% align:start
your household's suppression
of the bandits failed.

00:18:23.136 --> 00:18:24.505 position:33% line:89% align:start
As a result,

00:18:24.639 --> 00:18:26.541 position:19% line:83% align:start
our lands were attacked
because of your error.

00:18:27.307 --> 00:18:28.977 position:10% line:89% align:start
