00:18:48.963 --> 00:18:50.665 position:21% line:89% align:start
For all your trouble?

00:18:51.699 --> 00:18:53.500 position:38% line:83% align:start
I'm sure
we can reach an agreement.

00:18:53.635 --> 00:18:55.603 position:21% line:83% align:start
What's an appropriate
amount then?

00:18:55.737 --> 00:18:59.073 position:7% line:89% align:start
Perhaps, a hundred gold coins?

00:18:59.206 --> 00:19:00.440 position:33% line:89% align:start
Well, count,

00:19:00.575 --> 00:19:02.242 position:24% line:83% align:start
it'd only be right
if you cover the damages

00:19:02.376 --> 00:19:03.678 position:21% line:89% align:start
to our villages too.

00:19:03.811 --> 00:19:06.380 position:10% line:83% align:start
You don't speak like a child,
do you?

00:19:07.115 --> 00:19:09.550 position:19% line:89% align:start
Fine then, a 130 coins.

00:19:09.684 --> 00:19:10.618 position:35% line:89% align:start
Try again.

