[panting]

00:19:13.121 --> 00:19:18.191 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:19:21.929 --> 00:19:23.131 position:21% line:89% align:start
A hundred and fifty.

00:19:23.263 --> 00:19:25.733 position:21% line:89% align:start
Hm. That sounds fair.

00:19:25.867 --> 00:19:28.036 position:35% line:83% align:start
Oh, Father,
do you agree with me?

00:19:28.168 --> 00:19:29.302 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes.

00:19:31.371 --> 00:19:32.674 position:41% line:83% align:start
[RETES]
This child.

00:19:33.206 --> 00:19:35.242 position:21% line:89% align:start
He's an exceptional.

00:19:37.979 --> 00:19:40.548 position:10% line:83% align:start
Perhaps the Lord of Morteln's
words earlier,

00:19:40.682 --> 00:19:43.117 position:10% line:89% align:start
were more than mere humility.

00:19:44.085 --> 00:19:47.522 position:13% line:83% align:start
