it is a small price to pay.

00:19:52.392 --> 00:19:53.895 position:16% line:89% align:start
A hundred and fifty coins

00:19:54.028 --> 00:19:56.698 position:16% line:83% align:start
and we avoid the risk of
damaging the king's trust in us

00:19:56.831 --> 00:19:59.801 position:13% line:83% align:start
for letting bandits escape
and ravage nearby lands.

00:19:59.934 --> 00:20:01.401 position:24% line:89% align:start
It could be worse.

00:20:01.536 --> 00:20:04.972 position:5% line:89% align:start
Father, look, a 150 gold coins!

00:20:05.106 --> 00:20:06.473 position:47% line:89% align:start
Hm.

00:20:09.811 --> 00:20:11.278 position:41% line:83% align:start
[RETES]
Perhaps, Pas,

00:20:11.411 --> 00:20:14.247 position:21% line:83% align:start
I underestimated you
because you're so young.

00:20:14.381 --> 00:20:16.517 position:10% line:89% align:start
I must admit you defeated me.

00:20:16.651 --> 00:20:18.418 position:33% line:83% align:start
Do forgive me
for the things I said.

00:20:18.553 --> 00:20:20.121 position:24% line:89% align:start
I got quite saucy.

00:20:20.253 --> 00:20:23.758 position:16% line:83% align:start
You know, I don't believe
