00:20:24.192 --> 00:20:26.259 position:21% line:89% align:start
An unfortunate lapse.

00:20:26.393 --> 00:20:28.963 position:35% line:83% align:start
I'm Pastry,
Casserole Morteln's son

00:20:29.097 --> 00:20:30.798 position:10% line:89% align:start
and the pleasure is all mine.

00:20:30.932 --> 00:20:34.001 position:24% line:83% align:start
I very much enjoyed
making your acquaintance.

00:20:34.135 --> 00:20:36.637 position:5% line:89% align:start
Pastry, huh. I'll remember that.

00:20:36.771 --> 00:20:39.574 position:33% line:83% align:start
That's right,
may I ask you one more question?

00:20:39.707 --> 00:20:40.775 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes?

00:20:40.908 --> 00:20:42.677 position:30% line:83% align:start
You made a face
when we had tea before.

00:20:42.810 --> 00:20:45.278 position:13% line:83% align:start
I thought you might've been
displeased by what you tried.

00:20:45.412 --> 00:20:46.581 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah?

00:20:46.714 --> 00:20:48.750 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Ow!
-Did it not suit your fancy?

00:20:48.883 --> 00:20:52.053 position:41% line:83% align:start
Oh, no,
the tea was most excellent.

00:20:52.186 --> 00:20:53.988 position:41% line:83% align:start
-But...
-[RETES] But?

00:20:54.122 --> 00:20:55.990 position:13% line:83% align:start
I just thought the cookies
that were served

00:20:56.124 --> 00:20:58.192 position:19% line:83% align:start
were a little too sweet
for my taste.

00:20:58.325 --> 00:20:59.827 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Ah!
-[RETES] Oh?

00:20:59.961 --> 00:21:02.063 position:30% line:83% align:start
When you serve
baked treats with a good tea,

00:21:02.196 --> 00:21:04.799 position:13% line:83% align:start
