with something less sweet.

00:21:11.139 --> 00:21:14.075 position:30% line:83% align:start
If you do that,
the cookies will enhance the tea

00:21:14.208 --> 00:21:17.344 position:10% line:83% align:start
and make the tea and desserts
a far more enjoyable pairing!

00:21:17.477 --> 00:21:19.346 position:27% line:89% align:start
Oh, my goodness.

00:21:19.479 --> 00:21:21.516 position:33% line:83% align:start
I'm impressed
by your refined palate.

00:21:21.649 --> 00:21:22.784 position:19% line:83% align:start
A great trick to reduce
